# JavaScript

Read [app/javascript/AGENTS.md](../../app/javascript/AGENTS.md), [docs/FRONTEND.md](../../docs/FRONTEND.md).

- **Ask before creating a new Stimulus controller.**
- Controllers in `app/javascript/controllers/<feature>/`; register in `index.js`.
- Files under 150 lines. No new npm deps unless explicitly requested.
- Do not run build commands unless explicitly requested.
